{"tid":1693000,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］男友飲醉酒周圍屙尿 點算好？","createTime":"2019-11-04T11:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T11:54:31.000Z","uid":284452,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bf8ebc76dc114a4d352b3597797c031d4bd93a64","tid":1693000,"uid":284452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:09:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我同男友上星期book左間酒店房<br />\n諗住同朋友飲完酒返去休息同啪啪啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁佢又唔輸得個啲人黎<br />\n一次飲左6杯 之後返到酒店都重清醒既<br />\n啪完攬住訓到5點幾 佢無啦啦拎張被起身走左去茶几個邊<br />\n佢起身我就跟住迷迷糊糊咁醒左問佢做乜起身？<br />\n<br />\n之後我聽到水聲 呆撚左 呆撚埋右<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爬左去開燈 見到條仆街對住個茶几屙尿 <br />\n我問佢做乜 佢又唔應<br />\n就走過去叫佢係忍唔到都屙係垃圾桶呀<br />\n佢都冇反應 重差唔多去完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後佢攬住張被返上床<br />\n我就嬲嬲地行過去同佢蓋返好被<br />\n再去廁所拎毛巾抹返<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再嬲住上另一張床訓（當日冇哂大床房）<br />\n起身佢重問我點解訓另一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想問下次如果男友唔止屙尿 重屙埋屎應該點做好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"19fe3ef232a30ca85f7dd1c2bb24c2e4c46be969","tid":1693000,"uid":190387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:10:00.000Z","msg":"不推文"},{"pid":"fcd15eb3da00c38c8ec47c613de0e453aae2bc84","tid":1693000,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:10:01.000Z","msg":"吉佢屎眼咪熄到佢個制囉"},{"pid":"7e9f61ccee9e4b91436f22d26e09db5c61062555","tid":1693000,"uid":190387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcd15eb3da00c38c8ec47c613de0e453aae2bc84","tid":1693000,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:10:01.000Z","msg":"吉佢屎眼咪熄到佢個制囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"gay post<img src=